<FIRST>r a PM-Obit-Raposo     02-06 0402</FIRST>
<SECOND>PM-Obit-Raposo,0417</SECOND>
<HEAD>Co-Creator Of Sesame Street Dies</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
